988
01:07:14,444 --> 01:07:15,612
Lindungilah bersamaku.

989
01:07:17,489 --> 01:07:19,115
Eraku sudah berakhir.

990
01:07:19,950 --> 01:07:20,825
Sudah habis.

991
01:07:27,374 --> 01:07:28,250
Baik.

992
01:07:29,542 --> 01:07:32,087
Mari berjuang sampai akhir.

993
01:07:42,222 --> 01:07:43,974
<i>Para dokter juniormu</i>

994
01:07:44,808 --> 01:07:46,142
<i>kini mengikutiku.</i>

995
01:07:48,228 --> 01:07:49,104
<i>Tapi Direktur,</i>

996
01:07:50,689 --> 01:07:51,898
<i>Bo-hun,</i>

997
01:07:53,858 --> 01:07:55,777
<i>aku tak tahu harus bagaimana.</i>

998
01:07:58,530 --> 01:07:59,864
<i>Dulu aku belum menyadari,</i>

999
01:08:00,740 --> 01:08:02,617
